                </div>
                
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <hr />
                    <p class="lead">
                        Welcome to Lexus Mortgages your first choice for mortgages in Spain.
                    </p>
                    <p class="lead">
                        At Lexus Mortgages we offer a comprehensive range of services to guide you through the process of obtaining a mortgage in Spain.
                    </p>
                    <hr />
                </div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div class="row" style="float:left">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h2 class="myshadow">About Lexus Mortgages</h2>
                    <p class="box">
                        Our wealth of experience ensures that you receive the best possible rates and conditions for your Spanish Mortgage.
                        We only recommend reputable lenders & negotiate on your behalf to obtain the best deal on a Spanish mortgage.
                    </p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="@Url.Action("About", "Home")">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h2 class="myshadow">Mortgage Process</h2>
                    <p class="box">At Lexus Mortgages we are fully experienced in the lending criteria´s of the Spanish lenders. We are often able to give an instant decision as to whether the mortgage would be approved.</p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="@Url.Action("MortgageProcess", "Home")">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h2 class="myshadow">Apply Online</h2>
                    <p class="box">
                        Our mortgage payment calculator is simple to use. All you need to do is enter the details of the loan amount, interest rate and the repayment term.
                        The loan amount is how much you’ll need to borrow, the interest rate is the rate advertised by the lender and the repayment term is the amount of time it takes to repay the loan.
                    </p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-info" href="@Url.Action("MortgageProcess", "Home")">Try it! &raquo;</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
